'''Xena Avramidis''' is a Greek actress and model. In ''[[Game of Thrones (TV series)|Game of Thrones]]'', she portrayed [[Whore (Breaker of Chains)|a whore]] in the third episode of season four, "[[Breaker of Chains]]".
